Residents, especially in the Helderkruin, Wilro Park and Roodekrans areas, must be on the lookout for a black BMW with four occupants. Various WhatsApp community crime-awareness groups have reported that the vehicle is highly active in the area, having been used in a number of crimes and attempted crimes. The latest incident was in Wistaria Street where the suspects derailed a gate. When they were interrupted, they fled. Anyone who spots the vehicle is requested to contact the police, your security company or local CPF immediately. No registration number is currently available.